<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1e293b; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
  <p>Dear {{ client_name }},</p>
  <p>Please find attached invoice <strong>{{ invoice_number }}</strong> from {{ company_name }} for:</p>
  <p style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 12px 16px; border-radius: 6px;">{{ description }}</p>
  <p>Payment is due by <strong>{{ due_date }}</strong>. Please quote the invoice number with your payment.</p>
  <p>If you have any questions, just reply to this email or contact {{ company_email }}.</p>
  <p>Kind regards,<br>{{ company_name }}</p>
</body>
</html>
